casebody.data:
No. 10-9637. Soloman Stanton, Petitioner v. Carol Adrianne Stanton, et al. 563 U.S. 1007, 131 S. Ct. 2924,

179 L. Ed. 2d 1245,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 3987. May 23, 2011.

The motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis is denied. Petitioner is allowed until June 13, 2011, within which to pay the docketing fees required by Rule 38(a) and to submit petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
